ntive evolution in these relations must occur prior\nto z~1.3. Having demonstrated the power of this modelling approach we are\ncurrently analyzing similar data on seven further objects to better constrain\nsuch evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2011 19:59:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Jul 2011 15:02:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
