t timescales from source to\nsource, they could represent a numerous class of Galactic massive X-ray\nbinaries, remained hidden up to now.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Mar 2011 13:27:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-04-01"}
